### 登录演示环境
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/mock-login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nickname": "today-plan-demo"
}

> {%
  client.global.set("token", response.body.data.token);
%}

### 获取今日行动页
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/home/today
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 获取总览
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/dashboard/overview
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 获取提醒流
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/reminders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
